{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"layer6-task","type":"text","text":"## Layer 6: Task + Worker\n\n**Folder:** `core/tasks/`\n\n**Flow:**\n```\nPlanningEngine → TaskStore → TaskWorker → Tools\n```\n\n### PlanningEngine\n- **Purpose:** Break complex → atomic tasks (2-5 min)\n- **Output:** Exact file paths, code specs, verification steps\n\n### TaskStore\n- **Purpose:** SQLite persistence\n- **Features:**\n  - Crash recovery\n  - Status tracking (PENDING/RUNNING/COMPLETED/FAILED)\n  - WAL mode for concurrency\n\n### TaskWorker\n- **Purpose:** Background execution loop\n- **Behavior:** Polls TaskStore for RUNNING tasks\n\n### Task Schema\n```python\nclass Task:\n    id: str\n    status: Status\n    file_paths: List[str]\n    code_spec: str\n    verification: List[str]\n```\n\n**Related:** [[Task Worker System]] | [[PlanningEngine]]\n\n**Test:** test_worker_dispatch.py, test_planning_engine.py","x":50,"y":1000,"width":550,"height":520,"color":"#e8f8f5"},
		{"id":"layer2-console","type":"text","text":"## Layer 2: Console Harness\n\n**File:** `core/runtime/console_harness.py`\n\n**Strict Contract:**\n- Contains ONLY: `run_console_agent(entrypoint_fnc)`\n- Interactive loop only\n- No agent creation\n- No session creation\n- No orchestrator imports\n- Forwards text → entrypoint ONLY\n\n**Thin Shell Principle:**\nThis file is intentionally minimal.\n\n**Common Violation:**\n❌ Moving logic here creates tight coupling\n\n**Related:** [[Console Harness]]","x":700,"y":-33,"width":580,"height":483,"color":"#e8f5e9"},
		{"id":"sector2-title","type":"text","text":"# Sector 2: Architecture Deep Dive\n\n**Detailed Analysis of 7-Layer Runtime Chain**\n\nEach layer's contract, responsibilities, and failure modes","x":50,"y":-220,"width":495,"height":120,"color":"#4a90e2"},
		{"id":"layer1-lifecycle","type":"text","text":"## Layer 1: Lifecycle Manager\n\n**File:** `core/runtime/lifecycle.py`\n\n**Responsibilities:**\n- Boot sequence coordination\n- Mode selection (CONSOLE/WORKER/VOICE)\n- Global resource warmup\n- Error recovery\n\n**Contract:**\n```python\nclass LifecycleManager:\n    async def boot(self, mode: str)\n    async def shutdown()\n```\n\n**Critical Failure Modes:**\n⚠️ Boot sequence error → System won't start\n⚠️ Mode mismatch → Runtime behaves incorrectly\n\n**Related:** [[LifecycleManager]] | [[GlobalAgentContainer]]\n\n**Never bypass this layer** - All startup must go through here","x":50,"y":-33,"width":590,"height":483,"color":"#e3f2fd"},
		{"id":"layer3-entrypoint","type":"text","text":"## Layer 3: Entrypoint\n\n**File:** `agent.py`\n\n**Contract:**\n```python\nasync def entrypoint(user_message: str) -> str:\n    # Routes message to global agent\n    # No boot logic here\n```\n\n**Critical Requirement:**\n- Must use pre-warmed [[GlobalAgentContainer]]\n- Must NOT create new instances\n- Must follow runtime chain\n\n**Fixed Issue:**\nPreviously created new orchestrator. \n**FIXED** by using `GlobalAgentContainer.get_orchestrator()`\n\n**Verification:**\n```bash\ntimeout 10 python agent.py console <<< \"hello\"\n```\n\n**MUST ALWAYS WORK**\n\n**Related:** [[Entrypoint]]","x":1380,"y":-33,"width":550,"height":483,"color":"#fff3e0"},
		{"id":"layer5-orchestrator","type":"text","text":"## Layer 5: AgentOrchestrator\n\n**File:** `core/orchestrator/agent_orchestrator.py`\n\n**Central Brain - All decisions here**\n\n**Responsibilities:**\n- Planning\n- Task creation\n- Worker delegation\n- Tool routing\n- Memory coordination\n\n**Input:** User message + global resources\n\n**Output:**\n- Planning requests\n- Task creation\n- Worker delegation\n- Final responses\n\n**Integration Points:**\n- Receives from Entrypoint\n- Uses GlobalAgentContainer resources\n- Delegates to Task system\n- Calls SmartLLM\n\n**Critical Importance:**\nBreak this → whole system breaks\n\n**Related:** [[AgentOrchestrator]] | [[Intent-First Routing]]\n\n**Test:** All tests in test_agent_orchestrator.py","x":1620,"y":515,"width":505,"height":430,"color":"#ffeaa7"},
		{"id":"runtime-golden-flow","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph TB\n    subgraph Layer 1\n        L1[LifecycleManager]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Layer 2\n        L2[ConsoleHarness]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Layer 3\n        L3[Entrypoint agent.py]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Layer 4\n        L4[GlobalAgentContainer]\n        L4sub[Resources:\n        - Memory\n        - TaskStore\n        - Providers\n        - Tools]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Layer 5\n        L5[AgentOrchestrator]\n        L5sub[Planning\n        Delegation\n        Routing]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Layer 6\n        L6[Task + Worker]\n        L6sub[Planner\n        TaskStore\n        Worker]\n    end\n    \n    subgraph Layer 7\n        L7[Tools]\n    end\n    \n    L1 --> L2\n    L2 --> L3\n    L3 --> L4\n    L4 --> L4sub\n    L4 --> L5\n    L5 --> L5sub\n    L5 --> L6\n    L6 --> L6sub\n    L6 --> L7\n    \n    style L1 fill:#4a90e2\n    style L2 fill:#5ba3f5\n    style L3 fill:#6cb5f8\n    style L4 fill:#7dc7fb\n    style L5 fill:#8ed9fe\n    style L6 fill:#9febff\n    style L7 fill:#b0fdff\n```\n\n**Complete 7-Layer Data Flow**\n\n**⚠️ CRITICAL RULE ⚠️**\n*Any bypass → Architecture violation → Must fix*","x":1280,"y":1000,"width":930,"height":1380},
		{"id":"layer7-tools","type":"text","text":"## Layer 7: Tools Layer\n\n**Folder:** `core/tools/`\n\n**Responsibilities:**\n- Tool registration\n- Schema management\n- Tool execution\n- Result parsing\n\n**Registration:**\n- Tools registered once at boot\n- Passed to LLM\n- Schema validation\n\n**Known Issue:**\n🔴 [[LLM Tool-Call Schema Mismatch]]\n- SmartLLM ↔ LiveTool ↔ Worker schemas inconsistent\n- Current hack: `strict_tool_schema = False`\n- Needs proper fix\n\n**Tool Categories:**\n- Memory tools (recall, remember)\n- Information tools (search, lookup)\n- Action tools (calendar, tasks)\n\n**Related:** [[ToolManager]] | [[Tool Registry]]\n\n**Test:** test_tools_*.py","x":640,"y":1000,"width":540,"height":520,"color":"#ffebee"},
		{"id":"layer4-global","type":"text","text":"## Layer 4: GlobalAgentContainer\n\n**File:** `core/runtime/global_agent.py`\n\n**Single-Brain Pattern Implementation**\n\n**Resources Initialized ONCE at boot:**\n1. **HybridMemoryManager** - Vector + FTS5 keyword\n2. **SQLiteTaskStore** - Task persistence\n3. **ProviderFactory** - LLM/STT/TTS providers\n4. **ToolManager** - Tool registry\n5. **Agent Registry**\n\n**Critical Rules:**\n- Resources created ONCE at boot\n- NEVER recreated per message\n- Prevents duplicate runtimes\n- Prevents dual-brain boot loops\n\n**Access Pattern:**\n```python\n# CORRECT\ncontainer = GlobalAgentContainer.get_orchestrator()\n\n# WRONG - creates duplicate\norchestrator = AgentOrchestrator(...)\n```\n\n**Related:** [[Single-Brain Pattern]] | [[GlobalAgentContainer]]\n\n**Test:** Import test must pass","x":1040,"y":540,"width":480,"height":430,"color":"#f5f5f5"},
		{"id":"global-agent-flow","type":"text","text":"```mermaid\ngraph LR\n    Boot[Boot Sequence] --> Life[LifecycleManager]\n    Life --> Global[GlobalAgentContainer]\n    Global --> Memory[HybridMemoryManager]\n    Global --> TaskDB[SQLiteTaskStore]\n    Global --> Provider[ProviderFactory]\n    Global --> Tools[ToolManager]\n\n    style Boot fill:#4a90e2\n    style Life fill:#5ba3f5\n    style Global fill:#7dc7fb\n    style Memory fill:#9febff\n    style TaskDB fill:#9febff\n    style Provider fill:#b0fdff\n    style Tools fill:#b0fdff\n```\n\n**GlobalAgentContainer Initialization Flow**","x":50,"y":570,"width":990,"height":430}
	],
	"edges":[]
}